<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Objective-C on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/objective-c/</link><description>Recent content in Objective-C on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/objective-c/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Swift Unrecognized Selector Crash Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/unrecognized-selector-swift/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/unrecognized-selector-swift/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="unrecognized-selector--unrecognized-selector-crash"&gt;Unrecognized Selector — Unrecognized Selector Crash&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An unrecognized selector crash occurs when you call a method that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist on an Objective-C object.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error originates from Objective-C&amp;rsquo;s dynamic dispatch system. When you call a method on an NSObject subclass that doesn&amp;rsquo;t implement that method, the runtime raises this fatal error. Swift&amp;rsquo;s type system prevents most cases, but it can still happen with Objective-C interop.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common causes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Selector typo&lt;/strong&gt; — misspelling selector in &lt;code&gt;perform(_:with:)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Missing method implementation&lt;/strong&gt; — method declared but not implemented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KVO issues&lt;/strong&gt; — observing key paths that don&amp;rsquo;t exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Notification center&lt;/strong&gt; — calling selector that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Selector typo&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; button = UIButton()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;button.addTarget(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;, action: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;#selector&lt;/span&gt;(tappped), &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;: .touchUpInside) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Typo&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Missing method&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;MyController&lt;/span&gt;: UIViewController {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;@objc&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;handleTap&lt;/span&gt;() {} &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Implementation exists&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// But calling #selector(missingMethod) crashes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: KVO without proper key path&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Person&lt;/span&gt;: NSObject {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; name: String = &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; person = Person()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;person.addObserver(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;, forKeyPath: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;nme&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, options: .new, context: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Typo&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: perform selector&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; object = NSObject()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;object.perform(Selector((&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;nonexistentMethod&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-compiler-checked-selectors"&gt;Fix 1: Use compiler-checked selectors&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;button.addTarget(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;, action: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;#selector&lt;/span&gt;(tappped), &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;: .touchUpInside) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Typo&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;@objc&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;tapped&lt;/span&gt;() {}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;button.addTarget(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;, action: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;#selector&lt;/span&gt;(tapped), &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;: .touchUpInside)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-check-responds-to-selector"&gt;Fix 2: Check responds to selector&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;object.perform(Selector((&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;method&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; object.responds(to: Selector((&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;method&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;))) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; object.perform(Selector((&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;method&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-selector-with-type-safety"&gt;Fix 3: Use #selector with type safety&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; selector = NSSelectorFromString(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;handleTap&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;controller.perform(selector)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;@objc&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;handleTap&lt;/span&gt;() {}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; selector = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;#selector&lt;/span&gt;(handleTap)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;controller.perform(selector)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-proper-kvo"&gt;Fix 4: Use proper KVO&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;person.addObserver(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;, forKeyPath: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;nme&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, options: .new, context: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;person.addObserver(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;, forKeyPath: #keyPath(Person.name), options: .new, context: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe selector usage&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ViewController&lt;/span&gt;: UIViewController {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;@objc&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;buttonTapped&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Button tapped&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setupButton&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; button = UIButton()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; button.addTarget(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;, action: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;#selector&lt;/span&gt;(buttonTapped), &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;: .touchUpInside)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Responds to selector check&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; myObject.responds(to: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;#selector&lt;/span&gt;(myMethod)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; myObject.perform(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;#selector&lt;/span&gt;(myMethod))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/ruby/no-method-error/"&gt;NoMethodError&lt;/a&gt; — undefined method (Ruby equivalent)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/thread-sanitizer/"&gt;Thread Sanitizer&lt;/a&gt; — data race detection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/memory-error-swift/"&gt;Memory Error&lt;/a&gt; — memory corruption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Xcode Build Error on Mac</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/macos/macos-xcode-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/macos/macos-xcode-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="xcode-build-error-on-mac"&gt;Xcode Build Error on Mac&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Xcode build errors include compilation failures, &amp;ldquo;Missing required module&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;No such module&amp;rdquo;, code signing failures, or &amp;ldquo;Build system not available.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Xcode build errors occur during the compilation and linking phases of iOS/macOS app development. They can stem from source code issues, project configuration, missing dependencies, SDK version mismatches, or code signing problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing or corrupt DerivedData&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Xcode version incompatible with project settings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Swift Package Manager dependency resolution failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Code signing identity missing or expired&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing SDK or outdated deployment target&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CocoaPods/Carthage dependency issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build settings conflict between targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="clean-deriveddata"&gt;Clean DerivedData&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;rm -rf ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/DerivedData
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Or in Xcode: Product &amp;gt; Clean Build Folder (Shift+Cmd+K)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="reset-xcode-build-system"&gt;Reset Xcode Build System&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;defaults delete com.apple.dt.Xcode
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Restart Xcode&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-xcode-and-sdk-versions"&gt;Check Xcode and SDK Versions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;xcodebuild -version
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;xcodebuild -showsdks
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-code-signing"&gt;Fix Code Signing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# List signing identities&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;security find-identity -v -p codesigning
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Reset signing&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;rm -rf ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/UserData/xcshareddata/XCIntents/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="resolve-swift-package-dependencies"&gt;Resolve Swift Package Dependencies&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# In Xcode: File &amp;gt; Packages &amp;gt; Reset Package Caches&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Or:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;xcodebuild -resolvePackageDependencies
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-for-build-errors-in-detail"&gt;Check for Build Errors in Detail&lt;/h3&gt;
